    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"beautiful\" thing doesn't change the fact that it's all temporary. if everything is just gonna end in nothingness anyway, the struggle to keep going feels like a lie. why do we even bother maintaining this existence if the outcome is always zero?",
